  "body": "### Component\n\nForge\n\n### Describe the feature you would like\n\nWhen running `forge upload-selectors`, forge should upload signatures from error types, such as `error Foo(uint256)`. This enabled us to use `cast 4byte <error>` when receiving errors back from the network.\n\n### Additional context\n\n_No response_",
