    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "This is already supported, `forge upload-selectors` uploads the specified contract's full ABI which includes any errors:\r\n\r\n`src/Counter.sol`\r\n\r\n```solidity\r\npragma solidity ^0.8.4;\r\n\r\ncontract Counter {\r\n    error VeryLongError(bytes, bytes, bytes, bytes);\r\n}\r\n```\r\n\r\n```sh\r\n$ forge upload-selectors Counter\r\nImported: Function VeryLongError(bytes,bytes,bytes,bytes): 0x0adccd39\r\nSelectors successfully uploaded to https://sig.eth.samczsun.com\r\n$ cast 4byte 0x0adccd39\r\nVeryLongError(bytes,bytes,bytes,bytes)\r\n```",
